cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the vulnerability of power systems to cyber attacks, specifically false data injection attacks. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also uses optimization algorithms to solve the attack optimization problem, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with numerical difficulties in solving the optimization problem, which falls under numerical analysis (cs.NE).
